  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 27-115-55, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO PROVIDE THAT A HOLDER OF A PACKAGE RETAILER'S PERMIT ISSUED UNDER THE LOCAL OPTION ALCOHOLIC BEVERAGE CONTROL LAW IS ELIGIBLE TO APPLY TO BECOME A LOTTERY RETAILER UNDER THE ALYCE G. CLARKE MISSISSIPPI LOTTERY LAW; TO AMEND SECTION 67-1-51, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO PROVIDE THAT IF THE HOLDER OF A PACKAGE RETAILER'S PERMIT IS A LOTTERY RETAILER UNDER THE ALYCE G. CLARKE MISSISSIPPI LOTTERY LAW, THE PERMIT HOLDER MAY SELL LOTTERY TICKETS; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
